            },
            "description": "Creates (or updates) a MySQL user. Credentials and primary IP are resolved from the deploy job. Idempotent — re-running refreshes the password and re-applies grants.\n\n- `username` must match ^[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_-]{1,31}$\n- `database` (optional) — if provided, the user is granted access to this database only; the database will be created if it does not exist. If omitted, the user is created with no database access. Must match ^[a-zA-Z0-9_]{1,64}$",
